<plot>Granmama lives for only two things: listening for her lottery numbers and doting on her grandson, Tommy. A local prison breakout upsets Granmama's routine and favorite radio broadcast. Because of a deeply broken heart and a wandering mind, Granmama mistakes a runaway convict, Robert "Bobby" Thompson, for her own grandson. Will she turn him in before he can take what little she has?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?418873</url></doc>
